      <h2>Registration Process Statement</h2> <br>
      <p>
        Welcome to AgroTech SL, your go-to platform for empowering farmers in Sierra Leone. Before you start using our services, 
        we want to ensure you understand our registration process and the terms that govern your experience with our application. 
        Please read the following information carefully to complete your registration successfully.
      </p> <br>
      <div class="card-content">

        <h3>1. Registration Process</h3>
        <p>Sign-Up: To register on our platform, click the "Sign Up" button on our homepage. You'll be directed to a registration 
            form where you need to provide your personal details, including your name, email address, phone number, and password.
        </p><br>

        <h3>2. Agreement Acceptance</h3>
        <p>Before completing your registration, you must read and accept our Terms and Conditions, Service Fee Agreement, 
            and Privacy Policy. These documents outline the guidelines, fees, and privacy practices that govern your use of our platform.
        </p>
        <br>

        <h3>3. Verification</h3>
        <p>After submitting your registration details and accepting the agreements, you will receive a verification email or SMS 
            to the email address or phone number provided during registration. Click on the verification link in the email or follow 
            the instructions in the SMS to verify your account.
        </p><br>

        <h3>4. Profile Creation</h3> 
        <p>Once your account is verified, you'll be prompted to complete your profile by providing additional information such as 
            your location, farming preferences, or details about your agricultural products. Completing your profile helps us better 
            connect you with resources and opportunities in the farming community.
        </p><br>
        
        <h3>5. Confirmation</h3>
        <p>After completing your profile, you will receive a confirmation message indicating that your registration was successful. 
            You can now start using our platform to access agricultural resources, connect with fellow farmers, and explore 
            opportunities to enhance your farming experience.
        </p><br>

        <h3>6. Important Information:</h3>
        <p>6.1. Please ensure that the information provided during registration is accurate and up-to-date to facilitate effective 
            communication and transactions.</p>
        <p>6.2. By registering on our platform, you agree to abide by our Terms and Conditions, Service Fee Agreement, and Privacy Policy.</p>
        <p>6.3. If you have any questions or encounter any issues during the registration process, please reach out to our customer support team for assistance.</p><br>

        <p>Thank you for choosing AgroTech SL. We look forward to supporting your farming journey and connecting you with the resources you need for success.</p><br>         
